---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | TheCloseReport">
  <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px;">
    
    <h1 style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 8px;">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>
    <p style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 40px;">
      Last updated: July 2026
    </p>

    <div style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8;">
      
      <h2 style="color: var(--text); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 12px;">
        1. Information We Collect
      </h2>
      <p>We collect only your email address when you subscribe to our newsletter. We do not collect names, phone numbers, or any other personal information through our website.</p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--text); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 12px;">
        2. How We Use Your Information
      </h2>
      <p>Your email address is used solely to send you the daily TheCloseReport newsletter. We do not sell, share, or use your email for any other purpose.</p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--text); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 12px;">
        3. Premium WhatsApp Service
      </h2>
      <p>For premium subscribers, we collect your WhatsApp number solely for delivering the daily market report. This information is stored securely and never shared with third parties.</p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--text); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 12px;">
        4. Data Storage
      </h2>
      <p>Email addresses are stored securely via Resend.com. We do not store payment information — all payments are processed via UPI which is handled entirely by your bank or payment app.</p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--text); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 12px;">
        5. Unsubscribe
      </h2>
      <p>You can unsubscribe from the newsletter at any time by emailing us at theclosereportdaily@gmail.com. We will remove you within 24 hours.</p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--text); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 12px;">
        6. Market Data
      </h2>
      <p>All market data displayed on TheCloseReport is sourced from Yahoo Finance. This data is for informational purposes only and should not be considered financial advice.</p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--text); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 32px 0 12px;">
        7. Contact
      </h2>
      <p>For any privacy concerns, please contact us at theclosereportdaily@gmail.com</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>